name: Headtogether Hypnotherapy
description: If you are feeling stressed, anxious or finding yourself too dependent on alcohol or food to get your through the lockdown, Hypnotherapy, NLP and CBT can help. I use these therapeutic techniques online with you to help you create change, backed up with studio quality recordings that you can keep to reinforce the work we do.  To find out more check out my website where you will find videos, books and blogs to inform and help you too.
